An excellent DVD and Soundtrack Boxed Set from an enlightened group of philosophers and writers. The idea is to be aware of your environment. Circumspect - look around you, and take advantage of the God given energies available. Every thought has a frequency the law of attraction. A Genie, "your wish is my command", life is a universal catalogue of harmony, happiness and strife. Be grateful and appreciate the accomplishments of others as experience for your own catalogue. There is one energy field here and outer space, visualize and materialize for happiness, well-being, financial worries and friendships. Our last frontier is not in space but in our mind........ it is still an untrained emotional energy. Author Jack Canfield explains the attraction of success well in this DVD with examples from Plato to Einstein, a spiritual feeling as power.
